    "Therefore, this method is most suitable for quickly establishing design concepts with clients, which designers can further refine and adjust to match the actual dimensions of the project site.",
    "This implies that the method needs to be used with manual intervention from designers to ensure the final design aligns with the requirements of the physical space.",
